Usage: dev-helper [options]

Description:
  watches for served files changes and emits page refresh in browser

Options:
  -h, --html			set root .html file (default: index.html)
  -p, --port			set port (default: 8080)
      --help			print man
  -s, --no-verbose		no console output
  -t, --new-tab     		do not interrupt websocket connection
